folder: Woodhaven Blvd & Booth Street, Queens, NY
text:
Woodhaven Boulevard, east side, between Booth and Wetherole Streets, showing the E. Reichart farmhouse of 1873.  It was still in the family in 1891.  Not there is another 2 1/2 story family house at the S.E. corner of Woodhaven and Queens Boulevards belonging to the same family.  It is this house that was in existence in 1873 according to the Queens Atlas of 1873.

April 1923

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
